title: BRAND NEW INFLUENCER: Be A Superstar In the Next Era of Social Media, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO285
itunes:title: BRAND NEW INFLUENCER: Be A Superstar In The Next Era of Social Media, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO285
description: The rules for social media success are changing. I'm a social media influencer myself & I employ thousands of influencers who represent my companies, & I can tell you this: the game is different now. It's so different that much of what used to work isn't going to work anymore. In this new era, if you want to build a focused & engaged following, leverage your platform for your business, & make millions off your personal brand...then you better take to heart what's in this episode & put it into practice.
